     C                     MOVELL1UKMM    P@UKMM
     C                     MOVELL1UKDD    P@UKDD
     C                     MOVELL1UBIN    P@UBIN
     C                     MOVEL'AKBR03'  P@FPGM
     C                     Z-ADDL1UZAR    P@MAIS
     C                     MOVE 'M'       PSTS    1
     C                     CALL 'ACHR01'
     C                     PARM           P@JBN1  1
     C                     PARM           P@JBN2  2
     C                     PARM           P@JBN3  2
     C                     PARM           P@JBN4  1
